    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged; the assessment team determined the overall evidence package is sufficient for the regulatory submission given the conservative nature of the single-condition test loading. Decision accepted with documented gap.",
